f'(a)=\frac{\pi}{2}\int_{0}^{+\infty}\left(\operatorname{sign}(y+a)+\operatorname{sign}(y-a)\right)e^{-y}\,dy = \pi\int_{a}^{+\infty}e^{-y}\,dy = \pi e^{-a}.
